# Claude Code harness state
# Track team-wide config (settings.json, commands/, agents/, rules/,
# pre-commit-checklist.md) but ignore personal state and cache.
.claude/*
!.claude/settings.json
!.claude/commands/
!.claude/agents/
!.claude/rules/
!.claude/pre-commit-checklist.md
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/.last_session_id
.claude/cache/

